    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "data": ":::header\n## Cvičenie 11.:cnt[a]\n::p[Základy rezolvencie]{.h4}\n\n:small[:icon[source] Prednášky: :xref[15.1]{.lec label=\"def.\"}, :xref[15.4]{.lec label=\"def.\"}, :xref[15.5]{.lec label=\"príklad\"}, :xref[15.6]{.lec label=\"tvrdenie\"}; :xref[15.33]{.lec label=\"def.\"} a následný príklad, :xref[15.6]{.lec label=\"tvrdenie\"}; :xref[15.35]{.lec label=\"veta\"}.\nZbierka: :xref[7.1.5]{.exbook label=\"úloha\"}, :xref[7.3.1]{.exbook label=\"príklad\"}.]\n:::\n\n:icon[tools] Zistite, ktoré z nasledujúcich množín klauzúl sú nesplniteľné. Nesplniteľnosť dokážte Rezolvenčným kalkulom, pomocou aplikácie resolution editor. Splniteľnosť dokážte nájdením vhodnej štruktúry.",
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "type": "text",
      "data": "::h3[:cnt[b]{.a})]{.h6.float-start.my-0.me-2.fw-bold}\n\n$\\begin{aligned}\nT = \\{\n        &(\\sym{barks}(\\vx) \\lor \\neg \\sym{dog}(\\vx)),\\\\\n        &(\\neg \\sym{dog}(\\vx) \\lor \\sym{bites}(\\vx)),\\\\\n        &(\\neg \\sym{dog}(\\vx) \\lor \\neg \\sym{barks}(\\vx) \\lor\n          \\neg \\sym{bites}(\\vx)),\\\\\n        &\\sym{dog}(\\sym{Rex})\n\\}\n\\end{aligned}$",
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "resolutionEditor",
      "data": "{\"language\":{\"consts\":{\"input\":\"Rex\",\"object\":[\"Rex\"],\"error\":\"\",\"symbols\":[\"Rex\"]},\"funs\":{\"input\":\"\",\"object\":[],\"error\":\"\",\"symbols\":[]},\"preds\":{\"input\":\"barks/1, dog/1, bites/1\",\"object\":[[\"barks\",1],[\"dog\",1],[\"bites\",1]],\"error\":\"\",\"symbols\":[{\"name\":\"barks\",\"arity\":1},{\"name\":\"dog\",\"arity\":1},{\"name\":\"bites\",\"arity\":1}]}},\"steps\":{\"order\":[0,1,2,3],\"allSteps\":[[0,{\"formula\":{\"input\":\"(barks(x) ∨ ¬dog(x))\",\"object\":{\"lits\":[{\"neg\":false,\"name\":\"barks\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"}]},{\"neg\":true,\"name\":\"dog\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"}]}],\"litsMultiset\":null},\"error\":\"\"},\"rule\":\"Assumption\",\"reference1\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"renaming\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"reference2\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"unifier\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"valid\":true}],[1,{\"formula\":{\"input\":\"(¬dog(x) ∨ bites(x))\",\"object\":{\"lits\":[{\"neg\":true,\"name\":\"dog\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"}]},{\"neg\":false,\"name\":\"bites\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"}]}],\"litsMultiset\":null},\"error\":\"\"},\"rule\":\"Assumption\",\"reference1\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"renaming\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"reference2\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"unifier\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"valid\":true}],[2,{\"formula\":{\"input\":\"(¬dog(x) ∨ ¬barks(x) ∨ ¬bites(x))\",\"object\":{\"lits\":[{\"neg\":true,\"name\":\"dog\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"}]},{\"neg\":true,\"name\":\"barks\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"}]},{\"neg\":true,\"name\":\"bites\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"}]}],\"litsMultiset\":null},\"error\":\"\"},\"rule\":\"Assumption\",\"reference1\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"renaming\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"reference2\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"unifier\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"valid\":true}],[3,{\"formula\":{\"input\":\"dog(Rex)\",\"object\":{\"lits\":[{\"neg\":false,\"name\":\"dog\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"Rex\"}]}],\"litsMultiset\":null},\"error\":\"\"},\"rule\":\"Assumption\",\"reference1\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"renaming\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"reference2\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"unifier\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"valid\":true}]],\"rank\":[[0,0],[1,1],[2,2],[3,3]],\"id\":5},\"inputChange\":{\"originValue\":\"(¬dog(x)∨¬barks(x)∨¬bites(x))\"}}",
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "type": "text",
      "data": "::h3[:cnt[b]{.a})]{.h6.float-start.my-0.me-2.fw-bold}\n\n$\\begin{aligned}\nT = \\{\n        &(\\sym{c}(\\vx,\\vy) \\lor \\sym{b}(\\vx)),\\\\\n        &(\\lnot\\sym{c}(\\vx,\\sym{L}) \\lor \\sym{a}(\\sym{L})),\\\\\n        &(\\sym{c}(\\sym{P},\\vy) \\lor \\lnot \\sym{b}(\\sym{P})),\\\\\n        &(\\lnot \\sym{a}(\\vy) \\lor \\lnot\\sym{c}(\\vx,\\vy))\n      \\}\n\\end{aligned}$\n\n:::aside{.note.p-0.bg-transparent}\n:icon[explanation]\nMožno budete musieť pre dokončenie rezolvencie (odvodenie prázdnej klauzuly) použiť faktorizáciu.\n:::",
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "type": "resolutionEditor",
      "data": "{\"language\":{\"consts\":{\"input\":\"L, P\",\"object\":[\"L\",\"P\"],\"error\":\"\",\"symbols\":[\"L\",\"P\"]},\"funs\":{\"input\":\"\",\"object\":[],\"error\":\"\",\"symbols\":[]},\"preds\":{\"input\":\"a/1, b/1, c/2\",\"object\":[[\"a\",1],[\"b\",1],[\"c\",2]],\"error\":\"\",\"symbols\":[{\"name\":\"a\",\"arity\":1},{\"name\":\"b\",\"arity\":1},{\"name\":\"c\",\"arity\":2}]}},\"steps\":{\"order\":[0,1,2,3],\"allSteps\":[[0,{\"formula\":{\"input\":\"(c(x,y) ∨ b(x))\",\"object\":{\"lits\":[{\"neg\":false,\"name\":\"c\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"},{\"name\":\"y\"}]},{\"neg\":false,\"name\":\"b\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"}]}],\"litsMultiset\":null},\"error\":\"\"},\"rule\":\"Assumption\",\"reference1\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"renaming\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"reference2\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"unifier\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"valid\":true}],[1,{\"formula\":{\"input\":\"(¬c(x,L) ∨ a(L))\",\"object\":{\"lits\":[{\"neg\":true,\"name\":\"c\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"},{\"name\":\"L\"}]},{\"neg\":false,\"name\":\"a\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"L\"}]}],\"litsMultiset\":null},\"error\":\"\"},\"rule\":\"Assumption\",\"reference1\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"renaming\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"reference2\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"unifier\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"valid\":true}],[2,{\"formula\":{\"input\":\"(c(P,y) ∨ ¬b(P))\",\"object\":{\"lits\":[{\"neg\":false,\"name\":\"c\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"P\"},{\"name\":\"y\"}]},{\"neg\":true,\"name\":\"b\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"P\"}]}],\"litsMultiset\":null},\"error\":\"\"},\"rule\":\"Assumption\",\"reference1\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"renaming\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"reference2\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"unifier\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"valid\":true}],[3,{\"formula\":{\"input\":\"(¬a(y) ∨ ¬c(x,y))\",\"object\":{\"lits\":[{\"neg\":true,\"name\":\"a\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"y\"}]},{\"neg\":true,\"name\":\"c\",\"terms\":[{\"name\":\"x\"},{\"name\":\"y\"}]}],\"litsMultiset\":null},\"error\":\"\"},\"rule\":\"Assumption\",\"reference1\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"renaming\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"reference2\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":{\"name\":\"EmptyError\",\"message\":\"This field cannot be empty\"}},\"unifier\":{\"input\":\"\",\"error\":\"\"},\"valid\":true}]],\"rank\":[[0,0],[1,1],[2,2],[3,3]],\"id\":4},\"inputChange\":{\"originValue\":\"\"}}",
      "comments": []
